doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')
        title Pablo Eckardt :-)
        // Bootstrap core CSS
        link(href='vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
        // Custom fonts for this template
        link(href='vendor/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:400,700,400italic,700italic', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        // Custom styles for this template
        link(href='css/freelancer.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
    body#page-top
        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top
            .container
                a.navbar-brand.js-scroll-trigger(href='#page-top') Pablo Eckardt
                button.navbar-toggler.navbar-toggler-right(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fa.fa-bars
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#portfolio') Portfolio
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') About
        // Header
        header.masthead
            .container
                img.img-fluid(src='img/battlestation.JPG', alt='')
                .intro-text
                    span.name Hello, I'm Pablo
                    hr.star-light
                    span.skills Software Engineer - Keyboard Connoisseur
        // Portfolio Grid Section
        section#portfolio
            .container
                h2.text-center Portfolio
                hr.star-primary
                .row
                    for project in modalsData
                        .col-sm-4.portfolio-item
                            a.portfolio-link(href='##{project["modalID"]}', data-toggle='modal')
                                .caption
                                    .caption-content
                                        i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-3x
                                img.img-fluid(src='#{project["imgLink"]}', alt='')
        // About Section
        section#about.success
            .container
                h2.text-center About
                hr.star-light
                .row
                    .col-lg-4.ml-auto
                        strong What is going on: <br>
                        p
                            | I am a Senior at The University of Texas Austin, and I will be graduating on Decemeber 2017. Throughout my education at UT I've learned about a variety of concepts such as Security, Software Engineering, Networks, Cyber-Physical Systems, iOS Development, and web development. In addition to that this Semester I will be working on Ethical Hacking and Big Data Programming on AWS. I've also found the time to learn about Linux System Administration, web servers and Frameworks. Right I focus my free time finishing sudofindstuff.com, and getting better at JS.
                    .col-lg-4.mr-auto
                        strong  A bit of my Philosophy: <br>
                        p
                            | I am a firm believer that one should love technology rather than loving a particular technology. Which is why I prefer learning several tools holistically. I believe that if one has a broad contextual understanding of different tools, its easier to specialize in any of them. Having an open mind to learn new skills is probably the most important skill anybody should have. <br>
                        strong  About Community: <br>
                        p
                            | To me community is a very important part of life. Whether you consider your community your class mates, or co-workers, or even the internet forum you visit frequently. I think that contributing to your community in meaningful ways is key for achieving happiness.
                    .col-lg-8.mx-auto.text-center
                        a.btn.btn-lg.btn-outline(href='https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ACUQW9kPbtwqVdi-ybaf2eIp_6mePVOe_Qh-tX97zmE/edit?usp=sharing' target="_blank")
                            i.fa.fa-download
                            |               My Resume

        // Footer
        footer.text-center
            .footer-above
                .container
                    .row
                        .footer-col.col-md-4
                            h3 Location
                            p
                                | Austin Tx
                        .footer-col.col-md-4
                            h3 Around the Web
                            ul.list-inline
                                li.list-inline-item
                                    a.btn-social.btn-outline(href='https://github.com/PabloEckardt')
                                        i.fa.fa-fw.fa-github
                                li.list-inline-item
                                    a.btn-social.btn-outline(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/pablo-eckardt')
                                        i.fa.fa-fw.fa-linkedin
                        .footer-col.col-md-4
                            h3 Contact Me
                            p
                                | pabloeckardt@utexas.edu <br>
                                | (512) 366-2516
            .footer-below
                .container
                    .row
                        .col-lg-12
                            | Copyright Â© Pabloeckardt.com 2017
        // Scroll to Top Button (Only visible on small and extra-small screen sizes)
        .scroll-top.d-lg-none
            a.btn.btn-primary.js-scroll-trigger(href='#page-top')
                i.fa.fa-chevron-up
        // Portfolio Modals

        each project in modalsData
            div( id=project["modalID"]).portfolio-modal.modal.fade(tabindex="-1", role='dialog', aria-hidden='true')
                .modal-dialog(role='document')
                    .modal-content
                        .close-modal(data-dismiss='modal')
                            .lr
                                .rl
                        .container
                            .row
                                .col-lg-8.mx-auto
                                    .modal-body
                                        h2 #{project["projectTitle"]}
                                        hr.star-primary
                                        img.img-fluid.img-centered(src='#{project["imgLink"]}', alt='')
                                        p
                                            !{project["description"]}
                                        ul.list-inline.item-details
                                            li
                                                strong
                                                | Type of Project:&nbsp#{project["type"]}

                                            li
                                                strong
                                                | Tools:&nbsp#{project["tools"]}

                                            li
                                                strong
                                                | Date:&nbsp#{project["date"]}

                                            if project["hasgit"] == 1
                                                li
                                                    | Source code: &nbsp
                                                    strong
                                                        a(href='#{project["git"]}') Git Repo
                                        button.btn.btn-success(type='button', data-dismiss='modal')
                                            i.fa.fa-times
                                            |                     Close


        // Bootstrap core JavaScript
        script(src='vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js')
        script(src='vendor/popper/popper.min.js')
        script(src='vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js')
        // Plugin JavaScript
        script(src='vendor/jquery-easing/jquery.easing.min.js')
        // Contact Form JavaScript
        script(src='js/jqBootstrapValidation.js')
        script(src='js/contact_me.js')
        // Custom scripts for this template
        script(src='js/freelancer.min.js')
